--- !u!114 &7610936346488390773
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 424039229669924107}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: fbeb6d65be27d3b40a131a1e4ace56b5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  steps:
  - message: 'Welcome Adventurer! I am Gizmo your guide. This is Atlas Research Facility,
      the hub where science meets adventure. '
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    animation:
      steps: []
      cycles: 0
      cycleMode: 0
      sequenceEase: 0
      useUnscaledTime: 0
      updateType:
        enumValue: 0
      e_expanded: 0
      e_cyclesExpanded: 0
    dontUseTTS: 0
  - message: "In this first chapter, we\u2019ll check and measure the Atlas Car parts
      that will take us on our mission."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    animation:
      steps: []
      cycles: 0
      cycleMode: 0
      sequenceEase: 0
      useUnscaledTime: 0
      updateType:
        enumValue: 0
      e_expanded: 0
      e_cyclesExpanded: 0
    dontUseTTS: 0
  - message: Before we finish building the Atlas Car, we must learn key skills to
      make it strong, safe, and ready.
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    animation:
      steps: []
      cycles: 0
      cycleMode: 0
      sequenceEase: 0
      useUnscaledTime: 0
      updateType:
        enumValue: 0
      e_expanded: 0
      e_cyclesExpanded: 0
    dontUseTTS: 0
  - message: "Accurate measurement is crucial in science because wrong data can cause
      cars or engines to fail, making today\u2019s lesson important."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    animation:
      steps: []
      cycles: 0
      cycleMode: 0
      sequenceEase: 0
      useUnscaledTime: 0
      updateType:
        enumValue: 0
      e_expanded: 0
      e_cyclesExpanded: 0
    dontUseTTS: 0
  - message: "In Lesson 1, we\u2019ll learn physical quantities (like length, mass,
      time, current), and errors in measurement (random and systematic)."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    animation:
      steps: []
      cycles: 0
      cycleMode: 0
      sequenceEase: 0
      useUnscaledTime: 0
      updateType:
        enumValue: 0
      e_expanded: 0
      e_cyclesExpanded: 0
    dontUseTTS: 0
  - message: Lesson 2, teaches scientific notation for writing and working with very
      large or very small numbers easily.
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    animation:
      steps: []
      cycles: 0
      cycleMode: 0
      sequenceEase: 0
      useUnscaledTime: 0
      updateType:
        enumValue: 0
      e_expanded: 0
      e_cyclesExpanded: 0
    dontUseTTS: 0
  - message: Lesson 3, covers scalars and vectors, including projections, components,
      negative vectors, and unit vectors.
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    animation:
      steps: []
      cycles: 0
      cycleMode: 0
      sequenceEase: 0
      useUnscaledTime: 0
      updateType:
        enumValue: 0
      e_expanded: 0
      e_cyclesExpanded: 0
    dontUseTTS: 0
  - message: Your mission is to measure every part of the Atlas Car correctly!
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    animation:
      steps: []
      cycles: 0
      cycleMode: 0
      sequenceEase: 0
      useUnscaledTime: 0
      updateType:
        enumValue: 0
      e_expanded: 0
      e_cyclesExpanded: 0
    dontUseTTS: 0
  - message: Get ready! Prepare for your pre-test to see what you already know about
      these topics.
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    animation:
      steps: []
      cycles: 0
      cycleMode: 0
      sequenceEase: 0
      useUnscaledTime: 0
      updateType:
        enumValue: 0
      e_expanded: 0
      e_cyclesExpanded: 0
    dontUseTTS: 0
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
